Cowboy LITERALLY stood there and did nothing while getting shoulder striked to the face. I'm not going to sit here and let people act like this isn't a thrown fight. Go and watch the fight again in slow motion. Cowboy LITERALLY stands and does nothing while getting hit. He doesn't block, he doesn't change positions, he doesn't try to get a hit in. He stands and takes a bloody nose because it was probably agreed that he would get bashed up a little to make it look good.
